<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1619">حَمَّادٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ عُمَرَ اشْتَرَطَ فِي وَقْفِهِ: أَنْ يَأْكُلَ مَنْ وَلِيَهُ وَيُوكِلَ صَدِيقَهُ غَيْرَ مُتَمَوِّلٍ مَالًا.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>